'''Hunter''' was a hide-and-seek game played by the youth on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]]. [[Galactic Emperor/Legends|Emperor]] [[Palpatine/Legends|Palpatine]] encouraged the children of workers at the [[Imperial Palace/Legends|Imperial Palace]] to play it inside the Palace. The game was thought to have originated with these children. These games were rumored to last as long as three days.

